Description: Papyrus fragment with traces of Coptic text written against the fibres (verso), perhaps part of EA75358. EA 75356, 75357, 75358, 75359, 75360, 75361, 75362 are mounted together.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380741) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380741)
